&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supporting month-end and quarterly close.&lt;/strong&gt; You’ll help record journal entries for payroll, benefits, credit card and employee expenses, prepaids, and accruals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performing and improving our monthly bank reconciliation process.&lt;/strong&gt; You’ll own the execution of this process and look for ways to make it more efficient over time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Triaging and responding to finance-related staff questions.&lt;/strong&gt; You’ll intake questions and concerns from GiveWell staff and be the first point of contact on the Finance team to triage and respond to those communications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supporting annual compliance processes.&lt;/strong&gt; You’ll contribute to the audit and 990 preparation alongside the Controller and Senior Accountant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
